            "title": "美軍擬打擊伊朗，原油9連升，布油創4年新高！黃金收復4600美元，美元一度升至99",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月30日，聯儲局鷹派按兵不動，內部分歧嚴重。美股開市前，美股指期貨升跌不一，納指100期貨升0.14%，道指30期跌0.43%，標普500期貨跌0.05%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cN4I40Sgc8M4f5Fau0nJIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/d22fa961d958097f27928a234c6682be.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAU/USD收復4600美元關口，白銀升超2%至73.18美元。美軍擬打擊伊朗，特朗普表示已拒絕伊朗在和談中提出的條件，並將維持對霍爾木茲海峽的海上封鎖。原油升幅收窄至1%，此前一度升7%，連續第九個交易日上升，倫敦布倫特原油期貨日內最高升至126.41美元，創下2022年6月以來最高水準，年內累計升幅超100%；WTI原油期貨一度站上110美元大關。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6d15e27a-6499-388d-b724-88b9eb68c16f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ee58xKa6k8pCbRNiqmh6DA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://d55-invdn-com.investing.com/content/b71eb33ee5f62ecf9262c4c4f581d42d.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美元指數沖高回落，日內最高升至99.1。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidd